{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/cows-milk-allergy-in-children/background-information/causes/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"62433689-0bf5-54f1-a4c2-61d6274cdd19","slug":"causes","fullItemName":"Causes","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 5d57bf0e-4a33-44ab-9a7c-f306aed3e671 --><h2>What causes it?</h2><!-- end field 5d57bf0e-4a33-44ab-9a7c-f306aed3e671 -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item fa9bbb0d-84d6-4de3-be92-25f361b69659 --><!-- begin field 15e549ed-daeb-41d7-9456-f5cec6c3d793 --><ul><li><strong>Cow's milk allergy is an abnormal immune system response to proteins found in cow's milk. The exact underlying mechanism is unknown, but it is thought that various genetic, epigenetic, and environmental factors play an important role </strong>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/cows-milk-allergy-in-children/references/\">Flom, 2019</a>]<strong>.</strong><ul><li>Immunoglobulin (Ig)E-mediated cow's milk allergy is caused when there is sensitization to cow's milk proteins, expressed by the production of specific IgE antibodies against cow's milk proteins, which bind to the surface of mast cells and basophils. Following exposure to cow's milk proteins, the release of cell mediators such as histamine is triggered, causing the clinical features of an allergic reaction. </li><li>Non-IgE-mediated cow's milk allergy is thought to be T cell-mediated.</li></ul></li></ul><p>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/cows-milk-allergy-in-children/references/\">Motola, 2004</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/cows-milk-allergy-in-children/references/\">Ludman et al, 2013</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/cows-milk-allergy-in-children/references/\">Martorell-Aragones, 2015</a>]</p><!-- end field 15e549ed-daeb-41d7-9456-f5cec6c3d793 --><!-- end item fa9bbb0d-84d6-4de3-be92-25f361b69659 -->","topic":{"id":"a5282e12-9e0e-5a93-bf1e-c47cb44993b6","topicId":"055e8853-0668-4ee8-bef5-d86e8a39b416","topicName":"Cow's milk allergy in children","slug":"cows-milk-allergy-in-children","lastRevised":"Last revised in December 2019","chapters":[{"id":"e95ad3f8-8ddd-57bd-8fe1-a01a59402ca1","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"fceefe8b-f1a1-54cb-add7-5660134a61f9","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"ff117841-0d0c-5d1f-ad22-a2d8db741006","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"0a17cde7-a3cc-580f-a5ec-e74a03694b87","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"e8251ee6-b8da-567a-b543-5efa4c24f074","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"5cd1ea49-3964-5480-beb5-1208ab83ecb4","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"6737a350-b49d-5d33-a999-d2a5f41c7f48","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"bb1f8ca2-c855-56ee-bc57-4b1b77c9a276","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"296bbdac-c210-5305-8b31-aabc917df09f","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"5c4984e6-3f82-5632-9d43-2766ecbdec62","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"52bb5ec1-cd13-5a6e-a889-5e1d7a9ffcf6","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"92a5493f-38a6-5d89-a3e6-bcf0d7bfa1d6","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"8bb88e63-0cf4-5025-8dd3-1041e3b9d9ea","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"ec87042d-84e0-5a22-97eb-f9c346e5f3de","slug":"definition","fullItemName":"Definition"},{"id":"62433689-0bf5-54f1-a4c2-61d6274cdd19","slug":"causes","fullItemName":"Causes"},{"id":"99c10d89-9bd7-5a68-